{"tid":1978644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】請正視廿二條事件","createTime":"2020-04-19T00:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T05:09:55.000Z","uid":259980,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fac6e6699523395516fab0797c7b807d91412991","tid":1978644,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T00:01:03.000Z","msg":"幾柒都好<br />\n佢叫得垃圾政府改稿<br />\n就已經唔係咩無proofread<br />\n就係決定咗要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打橫嚟</span></span><br />\n人地就係有呢個power<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好寄望咩國際嘩然社會嘩然有用</span></span><br />\n過去一年睇透晒<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理撚得你</span></span>嘩然<br />\n無機制抗衡下<br />\n中聯辦會明面上「合理地」干涉香港<br />\n<br />\n如果嗰陣都係工照返舞照跳<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好覺得一定會有攬炒</span></span><br />\n中聯辦齋搞政治<br />\n商家佬<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">未必會好大反應</span></span><br />\n至少喺第一單中共影響到商人搵食嘅事發生前<br />\n我唔覺得金融中心會有變化<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過去一年日日tg咪又係金融中心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n比起笑人柒乜乜物物<br />\n認真諗下中聯辦治港後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭模式應唔應該改變/調整好過</span></span>"},{"pid":"3782f895f0b8d7f9667f7e2587fe1dc9f9e6127b","tid":1978644,"uid":128570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T00:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb72ae33cc36a496cbbc81f9b22f80f4a705224","tid":1978644,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T00:20:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c813a13c1f38aaab505118